  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Game</strong><br>Side Decide is a relaxing puzzle game that harkens back to the wooden blocks of childhood. The objective is to roll a wooden cube to the end of the level. Each side of the cube features a different kind of shape and you can only roll onto a block with the corresponding shape and alignment. Rolling onto a circle allows you to rotate your cube, opening up branching pathways to help you achieve your goal. Teleporting, wildcard, and falling blocks all spice up the mix.<br>Can you achieve gold on all 121 levels?<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple and pleasing aesthetics based on children’s wooden blocks<br></li><li>Peaceful music that adapts to the player's progress<br></li><li>10 different block types each with its own unique mechanics<br></li><li>Gold, Silver, and Bronze star ratings for each level give seasoned player's something to strive for<br></li><li>121 levels to unblock, 363 stars to collect. Can you get them all?</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blocks!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/114e115ea6b6a1157eecce4ada2cc707.poster.avif?t=1631152572\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/114e115ea6b6a1157eecce4ada2cc707.webm?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/114e115ea6b6a1157eecce4ada2cc707.mp4?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/131ddcd85c7fc81e9c3af7768dbd3358.poster.avif?t=1631152572\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/131ddcd85c7fc81e9c3af7768dbd3358.webm?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/131ddcd85c7fc81e9c3af7768dbd3358.mp4?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/227810cb5932c9c89a05690cf6532d3c.poster.avif?t=1631152572\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/227810cb5932c9c89a05690cf6532d3c.webm?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/227810cb5932c9c89a05690cf6532d3c.mp4?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/6b48ea79d8784a993d15968466998853.poster.avif?t=1631152572\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/6b48ea79d8784a993d15968466998853.webm?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/6b48ea79d8784a993d15968466998853.mp4?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/5f208cdbc27cf0961593600533da7a4c.poster.avif?t=1631152572\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1081500/extras/5f208cdbc27cf0961593600533da7a4c.webm?t=1631152572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source